<h1>Southeast Asia Sees Staggering Growth, Food Violations Continue</h1>

<p><b>Hong Kong, July 8, 2015</b> – AsiaInspection (AI), a leading global quality control and compliance service provider that partners with brands, retailers and importers around the world to secure, manage and optimize their supply chain, today announces its 2015 Q3 Barometer, a quarterly synopsis on outsourced manufacturing and the quality control services industry.</p>

<h2 style="font-size:18px;">China Overshadowed by Astounding Growth in Southeast Asia</h2>

